snippet.title: Reem Shaikh: Childhood, Career & Chaos
snippet.description:
Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Hardik Swagat Hai! 

Aaj ke khaas episode mein humare saath hain talented actress Reem Shaikh, jo choti si umar mein apna acting career shuru karke sabke dilon mein chhaa gayi hain. Reem khulkar baat karti hain apne career ki shuruaat ke baare mein, aur kaise unka safar Colors TV ke saath juda raha.

Woh batati hain apne latest show Laughter Chef ke mazedaar experiences aur apne pariwar ke liye unka pyar aur apni maa ke saath apne gehre rishte ke baare mein. Reem apne old-school nature aur emotional side ko bhi share karti hain, jo unhe alag banata hai.

localized.title: Reem Shaikh: Childhood, Career & Chaos
localized.description:
Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Hardik Swagat Hai! 

Aaj ke khaas episode mein humare saath hain talented actress Reem Shaikh, jo choti si umar mein apna acting career shuru karke sabke dilon mein chhaa gayi hain. Reem khulkar baat karti hain apne career ki shuruaat ke baare mein, aur kaise unka safar Colors TV ke saath juda raha.

Woh batati hain apne latest show Laughter Chef ke mazedaar experiences aur apne pariwar ke liye unka pyar aur apni maa ke saath apne gehre rishte ke baare mein. Reem apne old-school nature aur emotional side ko bhi share karti hain, jo unhe alag banata hai. 

Yeh episode ek perfect mix hai laughter, emotions aur inspiration ka — Only On @bhartitv

snippet.title: அப்பப்பப்பா..அதிரடி தண்ணீ சட்னி! Kongu Famous Thakkali Thanni Chutney | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Recipe by : Tmt. Manonmani
Mono's Kitchen 
9952809354

Thanni Chutney
Ingredients

Tomato - 1/2 Kg
Onion - 3 Nos.
Green Chilli - 2 or 3 Nos. 
Cumin Seeds - 1 Tsp
Mustard - 1 Tsp
Coriander Leaves - As Required 
Curry Leaves - 2 Strings 
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp 
Chilli Powder - 2 Tsp
Coriander Powder - 3 Tsp
Salt - To Taste
Oil - 50ml


My Amazon Store { My Picks and Recommended Product }
https://www.amazon.in/shop/chefdeenaskitchen

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Nautapa 2025 On Monsoon | नौतपा क्या होता है और इसका मॉनसून से क्या है संबंध । Kisan India
snippet.description:
नौतपा 2025 को लेकर मौसम में आया अनोखा बदलाव! इस साल नौतपा के दौरान गर्मी का तेज असर कम देखने को मिला, जिससे अब मॉनसून के पैटर्न में भी बदलाव की संभावना जताई जा रही है।
इस वीडियो में जानिए:
नौतपा क्या होता है और इसका मॉनसून से क्या संबंध है?
Kisan India खेती-किसानी से जुड़ी हर महत्वपूर्ण जानकारी प्रदान करता है। यहां आपको नवीनतम कृषि तकनीक, सरकारी योजनाएं, बाजार भाव, विशेषज्ञ सलाह और बहुत कुछ मिलेगा। हमारे साथ जुड़कर आप खेती से संबंधित सभी जरूरी खबरें, अपडेट्स और टिप्स पा सकते हैं। खेती को और भी लाभकारी बनाने के लिए हमारे वीडियो को जरूर देखें!

snippet.description:

Episode 4391: Bhide Pe Aarop
--------------------------------------------------------
As Bhide prepares for a day out with his wife, Popatlal unexpectedly calls for a meeting and accuses him of something serious. What has triggered Popatlal's anger this time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 4391
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4409: Investment Ki Chinta
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone in the colony is excited about their new investment, but Bapuji advises Jethalal to wait until the profits actually reach his account. What will Jethalal discover when he finally tries to withdraw the money?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4409 | 28 May 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sise ki meri jawani
Mai hu pari Aasmani
Aankhe Gulabi Gulabi
Masti bhari jindagani 

Lakho diwana Mare Rojana 
Dil Hola Bekarar 
Aaela Jab Chal Ke 

Karela Bawal Tohar Ghaghara Jalidar 
Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

Ho Jaye Da Pyar 
Kahe Karelu Inkar 
Jawani Jhal Jhal Jhalke

Dhakate Dhakan Hamar 80 Ke Raftar 
Kabo Halke Halke

Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

Aag Lage style Par 
Hola Murder Smile Par

Mohabat Ba Bhar Bhar Ke

Karejawa Dhak Dhak Dhadke
Odhaniya Sar Sarke

Dekhela Tab Tab 
Penhila Jab Jab 
Hathawa Me Chatkar 
Chudi Lalke Lalke

Gora Gora Face Pa 
Gori Kala Kala Bal 
Lipistik Purple Ke

Dhakate Dil E Hamar 
80 Ke Raftar 
Kabo Halke Halke

Chauraha Kabo Gali pa
Aawe Bhaura eh Kali Pa

Umariya Nanhki Nanhki
Satelu Tanki Tanki 
Marat Balu Kankhi Kankhi 
Ta Manawa Sanaki Sanki 

Sahal Na Jala nahi Sohala 
Hamara Ke Bewahar Aashu Neelkamal Ke 

Jab Se Tohake Dekhale Bani 
Chadhata Bukhar 
Jarurat Ba Phal Ke 

Karela Bawal Tohar Ghaghara Jalidar 
Dupatta Mal Mal Ke

snippet.title: The World Champion vs World no.2 | Gukesh vs Hikaru Nakamura | Norway Chess 2025
snippet.description:
D. Gukesh had a dismal start to Norway Chess. He lost 2 classical games - to Magnus Carlsen and Arjun Erigaisi. Meanwhile Hikaru Nakamura started off beautifully with a win over Caruana and also beat Magnus in an Armageddon! It was now time for the World Champion Gukesh and World no.2 Hikaru to meet in round 3. It was also the last day of Gukesh as an 18-year-old as 29th of May was his birthday! How would the final game of his 18th year be? Check out the battle along with the commentary by IM Sagar Shah.

Video: ChessBase India 
Shot by Aditya Sur Roy, Edited by Ravindra Potawad

hi.title: विश्व चैंपियन बनाम विश्व नंबर 2 | गुकेश बनाम हिकारू नाकामुरा | नॉर्वे शतरंज 2025
hi.description:
डी. गुकेश की नॉर्वे शतरंज में शुरुआत निराशाजनक रही। वे दो क्लासिकल गेम हार गए - मैग्नस कार्लसन और अर्जुन एरिगैसी से। इस बीच हिकारू नाकामुरा ने कारुआना पर जीत के साथ शानदार शुरुआत की और आर्मगेडन में मैग्नस को भी हराया! अब विश्व चैंपियन गुकेश और विश्व नंबर 2 हिकारू के बीच तीसरे राउंड में मुकाबला होने वाला था। 18 वर्षीय गुकेश का यह आखिरी दिन भी था क्योंकि 29 मई को उनका जन्मदिन था! उनके 18वें साल का आखिरी गेम कैसा होगा? आईएम सागर शाह की कमेंट्री के साथ मुकाबला देखें। वीडियो: चेसबेस इंडिया
आदित्य सुर रॉय द्वारा शूट, रवींद्र पोटावाड द्वारा संपादित

it.description:

Nel frattempo, Hikaru Nakamura ha iniziato alla grande con una vittoria su Caruana e ha battuto anche Magnus in un Armageddon! Era giunto il momento per il campione del mondo Gukesh e il numero due al mondo Hikaru di incontrarsi al terzo turno. Era anche l'ultimo giorno di Gukesh a 18 anni, dato che il 29 maggio era il suo compleanno! Come sarebbe stata l'ultima partita del suo 18° anno? Guarda la battaglia con il commento del MI Sagar Shah.

Video: ChessBase India
Foto di Aditya Sur Roy, montaggio di Ravindra Potawad

de-DE.title: Der Weltmeister gegen die Nummer 2 der Welt | Gukesh gegen Hikaru Nakamura | Norway Chess 2025
de-DE.description:
D. Gukesh hatte einen miserablen Start beim Norway Chess. Er verlor zwei klassische Partien – gegen Magnus Carlsen und Arjun Erigaisi. Hikaru Nakamura hingegen legte einen glänzenden Start mit einem Sieg über Caruana hin und besiegte Magnus auch im Armageddon! Nun trafen Weltmeister Gukesh und die Nummer 2 der Welt, Hikaru, in Runde 3 aufeinander. Es war zugleich Gukes letzter Tag als 18-Jähriger, denn der 29. Mai war sein Geburtstag! Wie würde die letzte Partie seines 18. Lebensjahres aussehen? Sehen Sie sich den Kampf mit dem Kommentar von IM Sagar Shah an.

Agar aap besan cleanser vs daily facewash ke beech confuse hain, toh yahaan milega natural aur chemical-free solution jise aap used besan for 5 days tak try karke farq mehsoos kar sakte hain.

Jo log face wash kaise banaye ya घर पर फेस वाश कैसे बनाएं soch rahe hain, unke liye yahaan hai ek effective diy natural face wash jo ghar ke ingredients se banega jaise besan, multani mitti, aur kuch aur kitchen ke nuskhe. snippet.title: Driver के बारे में जानकर Jetha क्यों हुआ Shock? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha Jasoos
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Everyone argues over the unaddressed tempo in the Gokuldham Society. Bapuji intervenes and asks them to come up with a solution rather than arguing with each other. Jethalal has a heartfelt conversation with his grandfather. Later, he revisits memories of the Republic Day celebration and decides to call Babitaji to appreciate Mahila Mandal's efforts for the preparations. Jethalal reads the letter to Babitaji that she found in Iyer's book. It was a love letter that he translates completely for Babitaji. Later, Jethalal's fear comes true, when Sundar arrives at his home and starts dancing.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2025 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch episodes from 'Jetha Jasoos' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?
list=PLn5vww_8o5Ku3tHY5oVV9jcxOqy9fOVW7

Driver के बारे में जानकर Jetha क्यों हुआ Shock? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha Jasoos

snippet.title: Stolen - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Stolen Official Trailer
Starring Abhishek Banerjee, Mia Maelzer, Shubham Vardhan, Harish Khanna, Sahidur Rahaman 
Written by Karan Tejpal, Swapnil Salkar “Agadbumb”, Gaurav Dhingra 
Directed by Karan Tejpal 
Executive Producers - Anurag Kashyap, Kiran Rao, Nikkhil Advani, Vikramaditya Motwane 
Production house -Jungle Book Studio 
Produced by Gaurav Dhingra 
Dialogues by Shubham Vardhan, Swapnil Salkar “Agadbumb”

Official Release Date 4th June 2025 on Prime Video India

About:
Stolen is a gripping action thriller set against a stark, rugged landscape in the hinterlands of India. The story follows Gautam in the early hours of the morning at a railway station, where he has come to pick up his brother Raman for a lavish wedding. But their plans unravel when they meet Jhumpa, a frantic mother searching for her kidnapped baby. Raman insists on helping, while Gautam wants no part of it. Then, a case of mistaken identity pulls them into a deadly chase, where their lives hang in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.description:
वट सावित्री पूजा 2025 - Savitri Mata Aarti - जय सावित्री माता | Vat Savitri Aarti | Vat Saviti 2025 - सावित्री माता जी की आरती

ज्येष्ठ माह सुहागिन महिलाओं के लिए अधिक महत्वपूर्ण होता है। इसका कारण है वट सावित्री व्रत। दरअसल, ज्येष्ठ मास की अमावस्या तिथि पर वट सावित्री का पर्व मनाया जाता है। इस दिन महिलाएं पति की लंबी उम्र व तरक्की के लिए निर्जला व्रत रखती हैं। मान्यता है कि इस दिन देवी सावित्री ने यमराज से पति सत्यवान के प्राण वापिस ले लिए थे। इस पर्व में मुख्य रूप से वट वृक्ष की पूजा की जाती है। कहा जाता है कि इस पेड़ में ब्रह्मा, विष्णु और शिव जी का वास होता है। इसलिए इसकी उपासना करने से तीनों देवताओं का आशीर्वाद प्राप्त होता है।

localized.title: वट सावित्री पूजा 2025 - Savitri Mata Aarti - जय सावित्री माता | Vat Savitri Aarti | Vat Saviti 2025
localized.description:
वट सावित्री पूजा 2025 - Savitri Mata Aarti - जय सावित्री माता | Vat Savitri Aarti | Vat Saviti 2025 - सावित्री माता जी की आरती

ज्येष्ठ माह सुहागिन महिलाओं के लिए अधिक महत्वपूर्ण होता है। इसका कारण है वट सावित्री व्रत। दरअसल, ज्येष्ठ मास की अमावस्या तिथि पर वट सावित्री का पर्व मनाया जाता है। इस दिन महिलाएं पति की लंबी उम्र व तरक्की के लिए निर्जला व्रत रखती हैं। मान्यता है कि इस दिन देवी सावित्री ने यमराज से पति सत्यवान के प्राण वापिस ले लिए थे। इस पर्व में मुख्य रूप से वट वृक्ष की पूजा की जाती है। कहा जाता है कि इस पेड़ में ब्रह्मा, विष्णु और शिव जी का वास होता है। इसलिए इसकी उपासना करने से तीनों देवताओं का आशीर्वाद प्राप्त होता है।
